### Player-Playlist Assignment API Test
### Base URL: http://localhost:8000/api/v1

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api/v1
@token = YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================
### Player Playlist APIs
### ============================================

### 1. 플레이어 플레이리스트 할당 목록 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/players/1/playlists
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. 플레이어에 플레이리스트 할당
POST {{baseUrl}}/players/1/playlists
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playlist_seq": 1,
  "pp_priority": 10,
  "schedule_start_time": "09:00:00",
  "schedule_end_time": "18:00:00",
  "schedule_days": "1,2,3,4,5",
  "pp_status": "ACTIVE"
}

### 3. 플레이어 플레이리스트 할당 수정
PUT {{baseUrl}}/players/1/playlists/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pp_priority": 20,
  "schedule_start_time": "08:00:00",
  "schedule_end_time": "19:00:00",
  "pp_status": "ACTIVE"
}

### 4. 플레이어 플레이리스트 할당 해제
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/players/1/playlists/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### Group Playlist APIs
### ============================================

### 5. 그룹에 플레이리스트 할당
POST {{baseUrl}}/player-groups/1/playlists
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playlist_seq": 1,
  "gp_priority": 15,
  "schedule_start_time": "09:00:00",
  "schedule_end_time": "18:00:00",
  "schedule_days": "1,2,3,4,5",
  "gp_status": "ACTIVE"
}

### 6. 그룹 플레이리스트 할당 수정
PUT {{baseUrl}}/player-groups/1/playlists/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "gp_priority": 25,
  "schedule_days": "1,2,3,4,5,6,7",
  "gp_status": "ACTIVE"
}

### 7. 그룹 플레이리스트 할당 해제
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/player-groups/1/playlists/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
